Description:
   Crystal Burst is an early offensive spell available to the Magi. The
   caster condenses arcane energy into sharp crystalline shards and projects
   them at high velocity into the target. The crystals shatter on impact,
   causing piercing and slashing damage from the explosion of razor fragments.

   Crystal Burst is a staple early-game offensive tool for the Magi, offering
   reliable physical-arcane hybrid damage at low mana cost. The spell is
   straightforward in application and does not have secondary effects, making
   it a solid damage option when more specialized spells are not appropriate
   for the situation. Higher levels of Magi find it replaced by more powerful
   fire and ice spells, but it remains useful in situations where elemental
   resistance would reduce those spells' effectiveness.
